 E(aX) = aE(X)\\ Var(aX) = a^2Var(X) 
 E(aX + bY) = aE(X) + bE(Y) = 10000\cdot3.2 + 1500\cdot7.5 = \mathbf{43,250}\\ Var(aX + bY) = a^2Var(X) +b^2 Var(Y) = 10000^2\cdot1.1^2 + 1500^2\cdot2.9^2 = 139,922,500\\ SD(aX + bY) = \sqrt{Var(aX + bY)} = \sqrt{139,922,500} \approx \mathbf{11828.88} 
